qas.question: Despite being headquartered in Poland, the top-ranking operatives of the Warsaw Pact were from which country?
Which nation was in effective control of both political and military functions of the Warsaw Pact?

plausible_answers.text: the Supreme Commander of the Unified Armed Forces of the Warsaw Treaty Organization

qas.question: Who was also a Second Deputy Minister of Defense of the USSR?

plausible_answers.text: the Chief of Combined Staff of the Unified Armed Forces of the Warsaw Treaty Organization

qas.question: Who was also a Second Deputy Chief of the General Staff of the Armed Forces of the USSR?
Who did not dominate the Warsaw Treaty armed forces?
What committee handled the assigned multi-national forces?
